public class BoundedGrid<E>
extends AbstractGrid<E>

A BoundedGrid is a rectangular grid with a finite number of rows and columns.

Version:
May 27, 2015
Author:
Alyce Brady, APCS Development Committee, Cay Horstmann, Anu Datar
